《[[冰血暴_(電視劇)|冰血暴]]》（{{lang-en|''Fargo''}}）為一部由[[諾亞·霍利|諾亞·霍利]]開創，於2014年4月15日在[[FX_(電視頻道)|FX]]開播的[[黑色幽默|黑色幽默]][[犯罪小說|犯罪]][[詩選劇|詩選劇]]。本劇改編自[[科恩兄弟|科恩兄弟]]1996年的著名[[冰血暴|同名電影]]。<ref>{{cite web |last=Goldberg |first=Lesley |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/fxs-fargo-cast-eps-film-671050 |title=FX's 'Fargo' Cast, EPs on Film Comparisons, Anthology Format, Courting Billy Bob Thornton |work=[[荷里活報道|好萊塢報導]] |date=2014-01-14 |accessdate=2014-01-23 |archive-date=2014-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140119113112/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/fxs-fargo-cast-eps-film-671050 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

2014年7月21日，FX宣布續訂第2季10集。<ref name="S2 Premiere">{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2015/tv/news/the-strain-season-3-american-horror-story-hotel-oct-7-1201559078/ |title=FX Renews ‘The Strain,’ Sets Premiere Dates for ‘AHS: Hotel’ and More |work=Variety |first=Elizabeth |last=Wagmeister |date=2015-08-07 |accessdate=2015-08-07 |archive-date=2017-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171002220930/http://variety.com/2015/tv/news/the-strain-season-3-american-horror-story-hotel-oct-7-1201559078/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2015年11月23日，FX宣布續訂第3季<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvline.com/2015/11/23/fargo-renewed-season-3-fx/ |title=''Fargo'' Renewed for Season 3 at FX |publisher=TVLine |first=Michael |last=Ausiello |date=2015-11-23 |accessdate=2015-11-23 |archive-date=2015-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151124154134/http://tvline.com/2015/11/23/fargo-renewed-season-3-fx/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2017年4月19日至6月21日播出第3季。2018年8月3日，FX宣布續訂第4季11集<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/chris-rock-star-fargo-season-4-at-fx-1132056 |title=Chris Rock to Star in 'Fargo' Season 4 at FX |last=Goldberg |first=Lesley |date=August 3, 2018 |website=The Hollywood Reporter |access-date=January 26, 2019 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109022356/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/chris-rock-star-fargo-season-4-at-fx-1132056 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。於2020年9月27日至11月29日播出第4季11集。

